1 STATE OF OKLAHOMA
2 2nd Session of the 60th Legislature (2026)
3 COMMITTEE SUBSTITUTE
FOR ENGROSSED
4 HOUSE BILL 3298 By: Timmons, Schreiber, Osburn,
McCane, and Menz of the
5 House
